{"msg":{"list":[{"title":null,"userName":"超越自己","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-21","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98V9iaN8R5iaLkF9JcWqWIDTJC440yyndibiciakf0Z9HcX3RgCdrphoSgHsA1zFAJwzicBicgRlMbyPibe3R05BOyxW3vUb/0","content":"1.为什么很少有人能够坚持每天看书呢？<div>因为现在是信息社会，外界的干扰和诱惑太多。</div><div>2.为什么有了干扰和诱惑，就不能坚持看书呢。因为排除干扰和诱惑，需要很强大的意志力才能够做到。</div><div><br></div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":9060,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492786108000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"拂晓","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-21","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XjoaHgicBwkEgpMoWJGibfMLGVLZR1GicYjONncfpgpJEhHlq0p3GTleavwa5Qib31WRLHMqX1KDQGJUfu3qaRqmcH/0","content":"<div>题外话，从我的角度回答了下问题，然后发现了我自己一直困扰着的答案๑乛◡乛๑ 。</div>我是大多数的一员。<div>1.为什么我很难坚持每天看书？</div><div>因为我不知道看书有什么用。</div><div>2.我为什么不知道看书有什么用？</div><div>因为我无法将书本里的知识与实践结合起来，知行合一。</div><div>3.我为什么不能知行合一？</div><div>因为我感觉我缺乏一套有效的系统方法，来消化书本中的知识点，并将这些知识点运用到生活中去。</div><div>4.我为什么会缺少系统方法？</div><div>因为我习惯于填鸭式的应试式的被动学习方式。</div><div>5.我为什么会习惯这种被动式的学习方式？</div><div>因为我缺乏独立思考和判断的能力。</div><div>6.我为什么会缺乏这种独立思考和判断的能力？</div><div>因为我从未学习并有意识培养锻炼这种独立思考的能力。</div><div><br></div><div>写到这里，我觉得我接下来应该知道怎么做了。</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":9058,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492785984000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"世界和平","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-21","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6ZHicGpiaBbXJBHPwF06gsWt2mNFCuP0uIBKjbMQYoyYmdglI9Qnjnpw7ObJUvqIXtYI3GkoZ3DxzUwKQoZ9lSNjd/0","content":"因为容易分心并且具有诱惑的事太多了。<div>什么最容易分心最具诱惑力？-刷朋友圈玩手机</div><div>如何摆脱手机专心每天看书？-看书时间将手机关机，或者放到固定的看不到的地方。</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8845,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492743637000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"小米虫","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-21","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/TVwhicV1539IW2Fx75h6RibTIiaqkpuQb3LkZYAAouBQUtOUpO5ldoyQuhjWqKUpJPicpIfh8lQrafUGtlR2bfCnZxTVXrCxjiaFW/0","content":"时间都花费在其他地方 ，表象的意志力薄弱;外界诱惑多，比看书有趣或自我评估比看书重要;每本书得信息容易单一化，且获取书的途径少，花费金钱时间价值大;图书馆不够普及且书贵;公共教育投入资源少","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8777,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492730956000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"不完美女孩","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-20","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6adoic3GoppNoL7r6ACBRlDQ6lF2y6e8E1tVWytWTLz0qHTS2vh1FymrLcoP9HrGtWuYRSqt6FF70OTBaczb1aibK/0","content":"为什么大多数人很难坚持看书，因为大多数人没有毅力，对书没有那么赶兴趣","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8721,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492703866000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"利 利","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-20","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98UZYfXiaDTkrtYGZNlwpEjXbPicvH7AAXyBd8HW3DNauJTMlrSq4zLWI39uiaUe1ty9icySz7UBnoLoFicdr7Ficjy1Dx/0","content":"没兴趣呀。为什么没兴趣？网络可选择性更丰富且方便。网上可以听书呀，可以看书评呀。（总结:想看书的怎么都能看，不想看的各种借口）","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8489,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492675036000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"小爽","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-20","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/PiajxSqBRaEID1MzQhjHmclnTsOeAfKPiceXpes94NazHeS2jjfE8w5g0mvt0X5ybWAM330ft4djRSu4uicS6G1Kw/0","content":"why不能每天看书？-注意力容易被分散-手机、电视、游戏在身边时间流逝-怎样解决？固定每天某段时间入睡前或早餐后阅读，同时关闭手机，远离分神产品。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8362,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492658049000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"龙头（2月20日至5月20日手机停机）","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-20","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98WcW0GibueBEaGmtCDiavicDfLEBgyWiaMjmESKqBNK7OkKJPgsLZ4wNtpy7COiatciapkuibb9lGXhDANMAYTflt9G5AR/0","content":"学到的知识很快就忘了，没有应用，工作生活中没用上，不知道如何应用","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8207,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492632083000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"旺旺","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-18","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4AyzclynlAbgSxPPqHxq7MefqKHPZtVP1ff8Ct4JCvqsIKQCZeY8icBSPOicyy0MmLcNB6yzYjFEwNgN/0","content":"1.为什么大多数人很难坚持每天看书？<div>看书能起到立竿见影的效果，成效很难展现，正向反馈不明显。</div><div>2.为什么成效缓慢？</div><div>书本知识转化为能力需要一个过程，而且质量低的书很多，读到好书是一个概率问题。所以成效缓慢很正常。</div><div><br></div><div>解决办法:</div><div>1.改变认识，承认读书见成效是一个缓慢的过程</div><div>2.需要列一个书单，按计划读，每天不贪多，养成习惯。</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7919,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492472151000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"球状闪电","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-18","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ajNVdqHZLLCPB8632Nxuia6CTs7I9LbKdkG6NPFtfP9L6Fr0dibaM7qSNgmGkpnL2Ac6YEAnVmEsBzHAbu4IicjuQ/0","content":"1.为什么很难坚持看书？——因为受到的诱惑多（朋友圈、电视、游戏）<div>2.为什么会被这些诱惑——因为做这些是享受</div><div>3.为什么是享受——因为只需要被动接受、不需要主动思考</div><div>4.为什么不喜欢主动思考——把主动思考=痛苦，看书需要主动思考，于是看书=痛苦。</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7914,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492469427000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"DearJoey","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-17","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XjoaHgicBwkEulNjy5o4vdjgC6HelC4abo7BkcNeqcy4n9DodScEqh59eBlvtBgia5zkLuxX2wTf0fA4ZSxI1gPp/0","content":"为什么大多数人很难坚持每天看书？因为现在娱乐方式很多，很吸引人。<div>为什么现在的娱乐方式很吸引人？因为这些娱乐方式很有新意，能激发人们的参与感，并且人们能从中获得放松。</div><div>为什么人们不能把看书当成放松的一种方式？因为大部分人不习惯这样做，他们习惯刷朋友圈 、看微博。</div><div>为什么不能用读书代替刷朋友圈的、看微博习惯？可以，需要针对每个人的兴趣开出书单，培养对读书的热情。</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7845,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492409389000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"郭丽敏","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-15","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4Ay3J1MHPAxQGN6yrKdJbWI9X6xzmUKCPn78X0urjAKAQWicAAibcgQvrz2ribr8qfnCMNsbkBMjhIw9b/0","content":"为什么大多数人很难坚持每天看书？<div>因为没有可看的书。</div><div>为什么没有可看的书？</div><div>附近没有书店、不知道要看什么书。</div><div>为什么不去读书小组找书单然后买来看？</div><div>感觉没什么必要，不看书也能活的好好的。</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7721,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492227978000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"潇洒鳕鱼","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-14","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98UyLlHC2Q1gMdxzMwDhQicAb4RP8PgibVuS6OEZoCGk0aIWo8mMahY8wu6ic8YFFqdsInJgJAaxbe58CIgsSXQC94U/0","content":"<p>说实话，这个问题，我还真不知道能不能找出原因，但是不妨试一下吧：</p><p>W1：为什么很难坚持每天看书？——因为没有形成每天看书的习惯</p><p>W2：为什么没有形成每天看书的习惯？——因为把看书当作是一种很困难的工作</p><p>W3：为什么把看书当作一种很困难的工作？——因为意识里自动把看书从享乐这一范畴当中剔出去了</p><p>最后，想多讲一点点就是：如果直接把看书当作是生活当中正常的一种享受，一种娱乐，其实很容易就坚持下来，每天像看一集电视剧一样，把书拿出看半小时左右的时候，一天又一天，形成习惯自然而然就坚持下来了。</p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7710,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492180336000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Leo","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-14","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XpSLeBeWNiaSic0ds8BMCibGZ2OUAZx2wvLS7l0JfCujUnFH561QnYtbqvZs2sAcicsmYHVHeJSgYia20o2R8WfC0mn/0","content":"<p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">用5why分析法，分析为什么大多数人很难坚持每天看书</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">W1.为什么大多数人很难坚持每天看书？</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">A1.因为大多数人没时间；</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">W2.为什么大多数人没时间？</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">A2.因为大多数人工作很忙，时间都变成碎片</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">W3.为什么碎片时间不能看书？</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">A3.因为大多数人选择在碎片时间刷朋友圈或上网；</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">W4.为什么人们更倾向于选择刷朋友圈或上网？</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">A4.因为朋友圈或上网可以得到即时反馈。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">W5.为什么看书不能融入即时反馈？</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">A5.可以，只是需要有人设计出合适的产品</span></p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7708,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492177891000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Jenny","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-13","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6adoic3GoppNoIfMsKLER8Nypic0GAEMQNhWH5ILCc3l1sO0iaB8nCIc9BLEdxIThXGnNtM55ozuBic03EicuCPictyib2/0","content":"因为每天都会有其他事情占据读书时间。<div>为什么每天都有其他事情？</div><div>因为没有很好的安排时间。</div><div>为什么没有安排好时间？</div><div>因为没有计划。</div><div>为什么没有计划？</div><div>因为不知道怎么安排--》应该按照管关键度和解决度来做好时间安排</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7652,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492076797000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Frank Wan","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-13","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/PiajxSqBRaEJp53Pl3fVDMmrsYbiboicLLjY2xagaHEvwsU5VZbF8OtVEn6icIUepE2Oh8Lpo3wOSx3E8k066fZkfg/0","content":"为什么很难坚持看书呢？<div>因为每天各种事情充斥着生活，不看书也照样每天过的没什么异常感觉。</div><div>为什么不看书也没有什么异常的感觉呢？</div><div>因为忙忙碌碌没时间思考自己的生活也没有长远的规划和追求</div><div>为什么没追求不思考呢？</div><div>因为各种诱惑因素太多，而潜在的需求又被浮夸满足了</div><div>为什么浮夸满足了需求呢？</div><div>因为浮夸的文章更容易吸引眼球</div><div>为什么浮夸的文章更容易吸引眼球呢？</div><div>因为人都有惰性，愿意相信所谓的真言，喜欢看速效救心致富文，鸡汤安慰文，鸡血励志文</div><div>为什么这类文章传播这么好呢？</div><div>因为优质信息缺少传播者，人民的思维能力有待提升</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7639,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492064293000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"张梦路","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-12","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6ZaLoY2RXU5FZibDrTsS1osmryDqKeuAvlF9licJ4nKDicnJ1HjwXTbvxdlVJj5oBJgqhR72iaGMxLcib1jJGsyWnUnj/0","content":"<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px; margin-top: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"line-height: 28px;\">如何培养他们的内在驱动力和营造外在影响力？为什么大多数人很难坚持每天看书？</span><br></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 28px;\">因为他们主动或被动中断读书</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 28px;\">因为他们受影响？<br></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 28px;\">因为他们没时间、没计划、没形成固定的习惯。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 28px;\">为什么他们没时间、没计划、没形成固定的习惯？<br></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 28px;\">因为他们认为读书不重要、或者本身就没有坚持的习惯很难坚持一件事。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 28px;\">为什么他们认为读书不重要、没有养成坚持的习惯？<br></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">因为他们缺少内在驱动力（兴趣、利益）和外在影响力（任务驱使、生活环境）</span><br></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 28px;\"></span></p><p>如何培养他们的内在驱动力和营造外在影响力？<br></p><p>兴趣：从自己感兴趣的领域入手，从简单通俗的读物入手</p><p>利益：增加聊天的谈资</p><p>任务驱使：通过输出（可以从写吐槽写感想<span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\">开始，涉及书中的内容）参加线上读书会</span></p><p><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">生活环境：少关注些速食公众号、微博、新闻，可以从轻松娱乐又有干货内容的媒体关注开始。换个上进的环境（工作、生活、地区）。</span><br></span></p><p><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">习惯养成和维护：放在每日固定日程中（如吃饭时、洗衣服时、等车时听电子书）</span></span></p><p><span style=\"line-height: 1.6; background-color: transparent;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">不要刻意坚持而是享受或不在意（目前找不到更好的词描述）</span></span></p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7608,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492006953000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"柚子","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-12","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcKQ9yoT3nbNKdxAfx36YXu2S1KS39tFaY2Biaj1Ax9EC2EFm7YL9S2bhnYO900iaLz2YBl7tPsiaN5msXdt9Z7ibzrD/0","content":"为什么大多数人很难坚持每天看书？<div>因为没有养成习惯？</div><div>为什么没有养成习惯呢？</div><div>因为没有按照科学的方法形成习惯？</div><div>为什么没有按照科学的方法呢？</div><div>因为太想当然认为是个简单的事情</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7594,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491992106000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"文","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-11","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XjoaHgicBwkEuUJBibwaegwqwa7rXILx7WPapDW7tTnawmINtpCLZRonooMm0ezL1xuuMLrs1trOmgp0gmOpYOuk/0","content":"<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">为什么大多数人很难坚持每天看书？因为每天事情太多没有时间。为什么会没有时间？因为没有合理规划导致浪费了很多的时间，做了无用功。为什么没有合理规划？因为不知道如何去进行精力的管理且不了解关键可行矩阵。</span><br></p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7502,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491877321000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"敏","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-10","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4Ay36u84xJJa5xZVbSorVQsjiaRtdKff23d2pibDW0oSbVW3r0CUiaQtIg47Itf131L8acNXmLucqib4ibt/0","content":"<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">1.为什么大多数人很难坚持每天看书？</span><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">因为大多数人没有从小看书的习惯。</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">2.为什么大多数人没有从小看书的习惯？</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">因为过去父母没有这个习惯，家里没有书，也没有这个氛围。</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">3.为什么过去的父母没有这个习惯？</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(5